  @{fg shine}Quirks:@{fg text}
  As of version 1.09
  o Menus are not drawn in proper colors. Never noticed before because
    magicmenus was always running. (Reported by Dewee Olivier).
  o Requesters are not centered on main QLib window.


If you find any problems  or  have  desires  for  other features you  would
like to see please feel free to @{"Contact" link Contact} me.
@endnode

